<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[访问&nbsp;文件:/CN-1463.5/访谈记录：SCP-CN-1463-1-101]</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
